name: Psychedelic Jam #2 (Heaven meeting)
description:
Psychedelic Jam is a collection of 10+1 interactable NFTs. I want create a connection beetween me and my collectors and friends. I think that jamming togheter it's one of the best way to know each other. So i created a little background track and i would you to fill the rest of the song. Have fun and let's jaaam!


How to play:

The game works better on PC but it's enjoiable also on mobile. If the game is not loading refresh the page, this my take a while the first time depending on your device and network, but the next times you'll come back the page will be saved and it will load immediately.

The music starts ONLY if you click on the screen.

Use the numbers on PC or the buttons on your mobile device to play the keyboard, SPACE makes you trip, BACKSPACE brings you back from the space ;)



Only 10 jams will be released, the 11th special jam will be given to the the best jammers that will share their video jam on twitter tagging @ClaudioBel2


Peace and love.
